---
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_TITLE_EN, SITE_AUTHORS, NAV_LINKS } from '../consts';

const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-inner wrapper">
		<div class="footer-brand">
			<a class="footer-name" href="/">
				{SITE_TITLE}<span class="dot" aria-hidden="true">.</span>
			</a>
			<p class="footer-couple">WJ <span class="heart" aria-hidden="true">♥</span> GB</p>
			<p>WJ 与 GB，把一起走过的路、见过的光，慢慢存成一本可以翻阅的册子。</p>
		</div>

		<nav class="footer-links" aria-label="页脚导航">
			{NAV_LINKS.map(({ label, href }) => <a href={href}>{label}</a>)}
		</nav>
	</div>

	<div class="footer-bottom wrapper">
		<span>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} {SITE_TITLE_EN} · {SITE_AUTHORS}</span>
		<span class="made">两个人的途中记录 <span class="heart" aria-hidden="true">♥</span></span>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		margin-top: auto;
		padding: 4rem 0 2.5rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		background: var(--bg-subtle);
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.92rem;
	}
	.footer-inner {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 2rem;
	}
	.footer-brand p {
		margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
		max-width: 30ch;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}
	.footer-brand .footer-couple {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.45rem;
		margin-top: 0.7rem;
		max-width: none;
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
		color: var(--text);
	}
	.footer-name {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--text);
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}
	.footer-name .dot {
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.footer-links {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 1.25rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
	}
	.footer-links a {
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}
	.footer-links a:hover {
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.footer-bottom {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-top: 2.5rem;
		padding-top: 1.5rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		color: var(--text-faint);
	}
</style>
